{
  "stem": "7282.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so-- and I support the whole family till 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my sister, Sosie's husband was Mayer Magjenborm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Magjenborm, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My brother's wife was Erna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yosef's.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Erna.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother Nuson's wife was Kela.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister's-- the other sister's husband, was Leib Wenokur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's all what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my brother, Shepa, he had [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] two boys and two girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, two started to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The oldest son, my brother's-- the oldest son, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he went away the same as I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't know where and how.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He left-- of course, he was in Ostrog-- left there and got killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The younger son, by chance, I met him in the woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's my nephew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I met him in the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from then on, we went together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We've been together till they took me in the army from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Afterwards, he-- they took him in the army too, afterwards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he got killed in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it-- it's, I mean, it's caused before that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What-- when we went during the war, I mean, in 1939, the 21st May-- this was '41, in 1941, when the war started with, with Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's when we start to-- we start to run.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so-- but like I said, I met my nephew in, in the woods.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we've been together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And since then, we start to, to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We worked in one city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Germans is behind us, or what.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We, we, we stayed overnight, sometimes not overnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we start-- and we walked till we got into Shepetivka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In Shepetivka, that was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a central point from the-- from the trains, or what.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
